  "description": {
    "zh": "我就说吧，那个司机知道哪条路才是对的！我之后会按照那条路安排送货的，但是现在我还腾不出手。首先，我得处理那些乱杀我的送货员的人。我已经找到了罪魁祸首，现在就等向他们送上 Ragman 的问候了。\n\n在这件事处理好之前，我帮不了司机什么忙。所以我建议你去处理这件事。快进快出，早点完事。",
    "en": "I told you the driver knows the right paths! That's where I'll send the shipment, although I don't have time for that at present. First I have to deal with those who killed my couriers. I already found the culprits, so now it's for Ragman to send his regards.\n\nI can't do anything to help the driver until this matter is handled. That's why I suggest you take care of it. Quicker you start, quicker you finish."
  },
